# Full-Width Page Content

**Canonical doc:** [docs/conventions/ui/full-width-page-content.md](../../docs/conventions/ui/full-width-page-content.md)

Page shells use full main width (no root `max-w-*`). Lists use responsive grids or tables. List pages with toolbar: [list-page-toolbar.md](../../docs/conventions/ui/list-page-toolbar.md).
